g.text: Standard features:-Optimised suspension set-up-Anti-lock brake system-Straight line traction control system (not including steer inputs)-Regenerative braking capabilitiesNovus features-Use of drum brakes for emissions reduction-Incorporation of in-hub emissions capture devices

Requirements for vehicle dynamics:Comfort, Handling, Holding, StabilityCascaded specifics:Noise / Vibration –suspension & dampingHandling –minimising slip & reducing pitchHolding / Stability –low centre of gravity
